{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be sleek and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SaaS Product</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f44336; /* Lighter Red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1e1e1e; /* Dark background */\n            --card-background: #2c2c2c;\n            --font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-top: 4px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 3rem 0;\n            background-color: #0f0f0f; /* Even darker */\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Smooth scrolling */\n        html {\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Productivity Redefined</h1>\n            <p>Unlock your team's potential with our cutting-edge SaaS solution.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Streamline Your Workflow</h2>\n            <p>Our intuitive platform helps you manage projects, collaborate seamlessly, and achieve your goals faster than ever before. Experience a new level of efficiency.</p>\n            <a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Powerful Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Task Management</h3>\n                    <p>Organize, track, and prioritize tasks with ease. Assign responsibilities and monitor progress in real-time.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Real-time Collaboration</h3>\n                    <p>Communicate and share files instantly with your team. Keep everyone on the same page, no matter where they are.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Analytics Dashboard</h3>\n                    <p>Gain valuable insights into your team's performance and project status with our comprehensive analytics.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Customizable Workflows</h3>\n                    <p>Adapt the platform to your unique needs. Create custom fields, stages, and automation to fit your process.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"pricing\" class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h2>\n            <p>Choose the plan that best suits your team. No hidden fees, just powerful tools.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Pricing Plans</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Your SaaS Company. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}